{"ts":"2026-07-21T19:13:37.700Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"jf-59hr"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Honor output formats and survive Playback Reporting user-list failures"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"All usage-stats subcommands hard-coded Toon despite advertised global/local formats, and the installed Playback Reporting plugin returns HTTP 500 for user_usage_stats/user_list. Route every report through the shared formatter and fall back read-only to core Jellyfin users with explicit per-record provenance when only the optional plugin user-list endpoint fails."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":0},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["formatting","plugin","resilience","usage-stats"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-21T19:13:37.700Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-21T19:13:37.700Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-jellyfin"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":90},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"All usage-stats commands honor Toon, JSON, YAML, Markdown, Table, and Raw format selection; A plugin user-list HTTP 500 falls back to GET /Users and marks unknown plugin membership explicitly; Other plugin errors remain structured failures; Unit and compiled-binary live E2E tests pass without mutations"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/goal","value":"jf-mqpo"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/value","value":"Keep optional plugin diagnostics useful and machine-readable on imperfect installations."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/impact","value":"Removes a live E2E failure and a cross-format contract violation."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/outcome","value":"Consistent structured usage reports with a transparent safe fallback."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/why_now","value":"The mandatory live suite produced 176 passes and one failure at the plugin user-list endpoint."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"jf-gn5j"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/reviewer","value":"maintainer"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/sprint","value":"jellyfin-10.11.11"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/severity","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/environment","value":"Jellyfin 10.11.11 with Playback Reporting plugin; jf-cli compiled binary"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/repro_steps","value":"Run JELLYFIN_READ_ONLY=1 jf-cli usage-stats users; observe plugin HTTP 500. Run with --format json and observe hard-coded Toon before the fix."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/expected_result","value":"The command returns the selected format and remains useful when the optional plugin endpoint fails."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/actual_result","value":"The plugin endpoint returned 500 and the command exited 1; all usage-stats commands ignored the selected format."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/component","value":"usage-stats"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/customer_impact","value":"Agent pipelines fail or receive the wrong serialization format."}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"ec3a403c05f3de4fbb42a37f686d8137afca1441a3404a09f19aaf3a03377d0a","message":"Track live Usage Statistics resilience and format fix"}
